Don't have a match but to me that's a "wooden type version" of [Helvetica](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414192521/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/helvetica) Extra Compressed/Compressed.  
Some that might work for you here: WF [Eldon](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414192521/http:/www.whatfontis.com/WALDENFONT_EldonWF.font), RR [Gothic](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414192521/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/redrooster/gothic-rr) Condensed Bold/ [Railroad Gothic](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414192521/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/redrooster/railroad-gothic-rr), [Rama Gothic](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414192521/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/flat-it/rama-gothic), [Eckhardt Headline](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414192521/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/jnlevine/eckhardt-headline), CG [Gothic No.4](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414192521/http:/www.fonts.com/font/monotype/cg-gothic/no-4)

More similar fonts: Gothic 13 [http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/gothic-13/](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414192521/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/gothic-13/ "http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/gothic-13/")  
PF Fusion Sans Pro Black [http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/parachute/pf-fusion-sans-pro/](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414192521/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/parachute/pf-fusion-sans-pro/ "http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/parachute/pf-fusion-sans-pro/")  
Helvetica Inserat [http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/helvetica-inserat/](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414192521/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/helvetica-inserat/ "http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/helvetica-inserat/")  
Smart Sans bold [http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/mti/smart-sans/](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414192521/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/mti/smart-sans/ "http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/mti/smart-sans/")
